251
00:31:10,729 --> 00:31:13,493
Gregor. Gregor, wait !

252
00:31:13,565 --> 00:31:16,898
Helen, l tried. There was an accident.
l can't make it stop. Hurry !

253
00:31:16,968 --> 00:31:20,404
You can make it if you try. Run !
Up those stairs. Run ! Quickly !

254
00:31:20,472 --> 00:31:24,704
- Wait ! Wait !
- l'll throw you a rope. Run quickly !

255
00:31:24,776 --> 00:31:27,768
