- Oh, no !

258
00:31:35,587 --> 00:31:37,817
l'm sorry !
lt was an accident !

259
00:31:42,227 --> 00:31:45,958
Helen ! Enola !
Helen, l'm sorry !

260
00:31:54,973 --> 00:31:58,340
Shoot him.
Shoot him.

261
00:32:06,017 --> 00:32:08,781
[ Man Screaming ]

