- Run to the other side.

284
00:35:14,958 --> 00:35:18,086
- [ Gunfire ]
- Come on !

285
00:35:21,297 --> 00:35:25,393
- [ Shrieks ]
- Grab on ! Hold on, hold on.

286
00:35:25,468 --> 00:35:29,370
- [ Gunfire ]
- [ Craft Shuddering ]

287
00:35:29,439 --> 00:35:31,464
l'm stuck !
