288
00:35:31,541 --> 00:35:34,305
- Let her go !
- [ Gunfire Continues ]

289
00:35:35,378 --> 00:35:37,312
Just drop her !

290
00:35:52,128 --> 00:35:55,894
Turn the wheel.
The wheel ! Turn it !

291
00:35:55,965 --> 00:35:58,798
[ Gunfire ]

292
00:35:58,868 --> 00:36:01,837
That ! Come on ! Push it !

293
00:36:01,905 --> 00:36:04,567
- l am !
- Hurry ! Now pull !

294
00:36:04,641 --> 00:36:08,543
Push it ! Push it hard !
Push it hard !

295
00:36:08,611 --> 00:36:11,637
Okay, okay ! Now pull this !
Pull this !

296
00:36:11,714 --> 00:36:15,172
Pull ! Pull it !
Hurry !

297
00:36:25,361 --> 00:36:28,592
- [ Gunfire ]
- Enola, jump.

298
00:36:30,934 --> 00:36:33,368
- Look at me. Jump ! Now !
- Okay !

299
00:36:50,153 --> 00:36:54,988
Well, excuse me ! Did l say anybody
could leave before the battle was over ?

300
00:36:55,058 --> 00:36:56,992
- Did l ?
- No ! No !

301
00:36:57,060 --> 00:36:59,460
Well, do somethin'.
l hate sails.

302
00:37:08,771 --> 00:37:12,002
Hey ! Can you steer ?

303
00:37:12,075 --> 00:37:14,009
Can l trust you ?

304
00:37:48,511 --> 00:37:52,106
