Call him ''Charles.'' Charles !

308
00:38:05,695 --> 00:38:09,756
Stop him ! Stop him !

309
00:38:14,671 --> 00:38:17,196
[ Screaming ]

310
00:38:17,273 --> 00:38:19,264
Charles !

311
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:23,044
Adios, cousins.

312
00:39:08,958 --> 00:39:11,119
She's here somewhere.
Keep lookin'.

313
00:39:11,194 --> 00:39:13,754
[ Screaming ]
Stop it !

314
00:39:23,206 --> 00:39:28,803
- What you got ?
- Couple of heartbeats over there.
Aren't sayin' much.

315
00:39:28,878 --> 00:39:32,939
lf you'll notice the arterial
nature of the blood comin'
from the hole in my head,

316
00:39:33,016 --> 00:39:37,350
you can assume that we're
all havin' a real lousy day.

317
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:41,254
So here it is: l need to know
about that tattooed girl.

318
00:39:42,825 --> 00:39:45,123
First one that
tells me lives.

319
00:39:45,194 --> 00:39:49,961
- l saw a girl. l saw, l saw--
- lt was-- Sh-She had
a big tattoo on her.

320
00:39:50,033 --> 00:39:52,194
[ lndistinct ]

321
00:39:52,268 --> 00:39:55,169
You won.
Start over.

322
00:39:55,238 --> 00:39:57,365
l saw a girl.
l'm not sure,

323
00:39:57,440 --> 00:40:01,216
but l think she got on that boat
with three hulls.

324
00:40:01,216 --> 00:40:02,342
but l think she got on that boat
with three hulls.

325
00:40:02,417 --> 00:40:06,786
- The boat that cost me
a thousand G's of go-juice ?
- Yeah, the mute-o's boat.

326
00:40:06,855 --> 00:40:10,757
- Mute-o ?
- Yeah. He got these slits here.

327
00:40:10,825 --> 00:40:14,192
Like-- [ Laughing ]
Like fish gills.

328
00:40:14,262 --> 00:40:16,526
He wasn't really a man.

329
00:40:16,598 --> 00:40:19,260
A fluke of evolution.

330
00:40:20,835 --> 00:40:23,201
Oh, l'm sorry.
A fluke of, uh--

331
00:40:23,271 --> 00:40:25,671
- Evolution.
- l know !

332
00:40:25,740 --> 00:40:29,608
- No ! No, you said
you wouldn't kill me !
- Did l say that ?

333
00:40:29,677 --> 00:40:32,805
- Witnesses, anybody, did l ?
- Yes, yes, yes ! You said--

334
00:40:32,881 --> 00:40:35,406
- You said it.
- Oh, l may have.

335
00:40:37,452 --> 00:40:39,386
l may have.

336
00:40:40,622 --> 00:40:42,715
- [ Gasping, Screaming ]
- [ Gunshot ]

337
00:40:45,927 --> 00:40:48,191
We get to the 'Deez,

338
00:40:49,464 --> 00:40:52,763
tank up that sky boat;
send it out on patrol.

339
00:40:54,035 --> 00:40:56,731
We gotta keep an eye out...

340
00:40:56,804 --> 00:40:59,204
for that ichthy-freak.

341
00:41:22,964 --> 00:41:25,023
You been there, haven't you ?

342
00:41:29,837 --> 00:41:32,431
Dryland ?

343
00:41:32,507 --> 00:41:34,668
You know where it is.

344
00:41:35,643 --> 00:41:37,634
Yeah, l know where it is.

345
00:41:40,748 --> 00:41:43,410
