423
00:48:50,431 --> 00:48:54,299
All right, the only thing
that is important is the tattooed girl.

424
00:48:54,369 --> 00:48:57,770
We don't spare any go-juice
findin' her.

425
00:48:57,839 --> 00:49:00,933
We don't waste it anywhere else.
You cancel all those tractor pulls...

426
00:49:01,009 --> 00:49:02,874
and all that stuff
until later.

427
00:49:02,944 --> 00:49:04,912
You got it ?

428
00:49:06,447 --> 00:49:09,280
Dryland is the mother lode.

429
00:49:09,350 --> 00:49:11,477
[ Laughing ]
On your toes.

430
00:49:12,921 --> 00:49:14,855
Excellent.

