Enola !
Enola, come here !

433
00:49:52,393 --> 00:49:54,327
Come on !

434
00:49:56,331 --> 00:49:58,265
Enola, come over here.

435
00:50:11,813 --> 00:50:13,576
Hey !

436
00:50:15,817 --> 00:50:20,379
- What are ya doin' ?
