439
00:50:30,498 --> 00:50:33,899
- l drew it for you.
- You don't draw on anything.
You understand ?

440
00:50:39,474 --> 00:50:41,408
What--

441
00:50:43,645 --> 00:50:46,614
This is my boat.
l got it the way l like it.

442
00:50:46,681 --> 00:50:49,479
