459
00:52:22,443 --> 00:52:24,411
Helen, help me !

460
00:52:24,479 --> 00:52:27,073
Helen !

461
00:52:27,148 --> 00:52:29,173
[ Sobbing ]
Helen, help me !

462
00:52:31,519 --> 00:52:34,215
[ Gasping ]

463
00:52:37,692 --> 00:52:40,354
Helen ! Helen !

464
00:52:40,428 --> 00:52:42,953
Hold on !

465
00:52:43,030 --> 00:52:45,430
Look at me.
Look at me. Look at me.

466
00:52:46,534 --> 00:52:50,527
