470
00:53:03,084 --> 00:53:05,450
Hold on.
Okay, almost...

471
00:53:07,021 --> 00:53:08,955
there.

472
00:53:19,033 --> 00:53:20,134
Thanks. l swear,

473
00:53:20,134 --> 00:53:21,499
Thanks. l swear,

474
00:53:21,569 --> 00:53:24,129
if you ever touch her again--

475
00:53:24,205 --> 00:53:26,332
You son of a bitch.
Look at me.

476
00:53:26,407 --> 00:53:28,967
