483
00:54:11,118 --> 00:54:13,985
Don't hit the kid.

484
00:54:18,659 --> 00:54:20,820
[ Cackling ]

485
00:54:28,402 --> 00:54:31,303
Hey !

486
00:54:36,244 --> 00:54:38,337
Coward !

487
00:54:44,218 --> 00:54:46,482
[ Laughing ]

488
00:54:46,554 --> 00:54:48,886
Fuck !

489
00:55:16,350 --> 00:55:19,114
No !

490
00:55:21,055 --> 00:55:24,183
[ Groaning ]

491
00:55:30,865 --> 00:55:32,799
[ lndistinct ]

